<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>
<!DOCTYPE plist PUBLIC "-//Apple//DTD PLIST 1.0//EN" "http://www.apple.com/DTDs/PropertyList-1.0.dtd">
<!--
  Recall librarian — the Mini's always-on, phone-reachable recall front door (second-brain rung-1,
  graduated from the MacBook piece-C prototype to the always-on Mini). This is a LaunchAgent (gui
  domain), NOT a LaunchDaemon and NOT cron: Claude Code needs the logged-in claude.ai OAuth
  (keychain) context, which only exists in the user's GUI session.

  Install (Mini, as jefe — AFTER staging ~/librarian AND the test.sh smoke run):
    cp orchestrator/librarian/keepalive/ai.myndaix.librarian-rc.plist.example \
       ~/Library/LaunchAgents/ai.myndaix.librarian-rc.plist
    launchctl load ~/Library/LaunchAgents/ai.myndaix.librarian-rc.plist
  Rollback (instant):
    launchctl unload ~/Library/LaunchAgents/ai.myndaix.librarian-rc.plist
    tmux -S ~/.local/state/librarian.tmux kill-session -t librarian   # end the live RC session
  Edit the bootstrap path below if your runtime checkout is not /Users/jefe/code/active/myndaix-runtime.

  NOT KeepAlive=true: booleans restart-loop every 10s ThrottleInterval when the program manages its
  own lifecycle. rc-bootstrap.sh is idempotent, so RunAtLoad + a StartInterval recheck is the right
  shape — it re-creates the tmux session only if it has died, and refuses if parked.

  AbandonProcessGroup=true is LOAD-BEARING: the short-lived bootstrap detaches a long-lived tmux
  server + wrapper; without this key launchd reaps the whole process group when bootstrap exits,
  killing the session it just created.

  WorkingDirectory pins cwd so the dir-keyed CLAUDE.md identity + the .claude/settings.json fence
  load (launchd's default cwd is / — wrong identity / no fence otherwise). The bootstrap also passes
  the workspace cwd to tmux new-session, but this is the belt.
-->
<plist version="1.0">
<dict>
  <key>Label</key>
  <string>ai.myndaix.librarian-rc</string>
  <key>ProgramArguments</key>
  <array>
    <string>/bin/bash</string>
    <string>/Users/jefe/code/active/myndaix-runtime/orchestrator/librarian/keepalive/rc-bootstrap.sh</string>
  </array>
  <key>RunAtLoad</key>
  <true/>
  <key>StartInterval</key>
  <integer>120</integer>
  <key>AbandonProcessGroup</key>
  <true/>
  <key>WorkingDirectory</key>
  <string>/Users/jefe/librarian</string>
  <key>StandardOutPath</key>
  <string>/Users/jefe/.myndaix/orchestrator/librarian/rc-keepalive.out</string>
  <key>StandardErrorPath</key>
  <string>/Users/jefe/.myndaix/orchestrator/librarian/rc-keepalive.out</string>
</dict>
</plist>
